WWW::Bizowie::API
====================

Perl interface to the Bizowie.com API

INSTALLATION

To install this module, type the following:

perl Makefile.pl
make
make test
make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    WWW::Bizowie::API::Response
    LWP::UserAgent
    Mo
    HTTP::Request::Common
    Try::Tiny
    JSON

